public java.lang.String tagsToXMLPattern()
Returns the pattern's tag sequence with XML markup. Format: <pattern type subtype relations minscore maxscore>pattern</pattern> Default values for the attributes are: type="unknown" subtype="unknown" relations="0,0,0" minscore="0" maxscore="1000"
